com.google.gwt.user.client.dnd
Class AdapterMouseListenerCollection

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gwt.user.client.dnd.AdapterMouseListenerCollection

public class AdapterMouseListenerCollection
extends java.lang.Object

A helper class which allows to implement a SourcesMouseEvents interface. This subclass of Vector assumes that all objects added to it will be of type MouseListener. It is using delegation instead of inheritance ; this allows to implements a MouseListener, for example to any Widget, without having to implement a MouseListenerCollection directly in a widget class.
